            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>能率亞洲(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:7777:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/7777\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">7777-TW</a>)27日11:33上漲3.2元，股價漲停報35.35元，委買7,000張、委賣7,000張，成交7,202張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為創業投資業。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>能率亞洲(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:7777:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/7777\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">7777-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲25.1%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲2.55%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+463 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+375 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+88 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
